{"tid":2499951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瑞典歌手The Merciful Descendant為香港作歌 惹來網民關注","createTime":"2021-04-22T09:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T11:45:09.000Z","uid":364068,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9d08c4aeb69514bd1298addddd662737874a11b8","tid":2499951,"uid":364068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:12:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210421/QGAOK7TVMNEL7IK4PJXDGS5B3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210421%2FQGAOK7TVMNEL7IK4PJXDGS5B3I&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClncVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=37ee7582\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210421%2FQGAOK7TVMNEL7IK4PJXDGS5B3I&h=b14a1795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210421/QGAOK7TVMNEL7IK4PJXDGS5B3I</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有隊瑞典Band出咗首歌講香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2497971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2497971</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CNioqaklZaQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNioqaklZaQ%2F&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClncVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=7292f304\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCNioqaklZaQ%2F&h=c0d8df0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CNioqaklZaQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n而聽歌嘅就可以去佢哋嘅SoundCloud, YouTube, 或者喺Apple Music 或者Spotify 到聽<br />\nSoundCloud:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?q=the%20merciful%20descendants&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;oe=utf-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dthe%2520merciful%2520descendants%26ie%3Dutf-8%26oe%3Dutf-8&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClncVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=45a3eb04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/search?q=the%20merciful%20descendants&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;oe=utf-8</a><br />\n<br />\nYouTube<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCXax9xkuopIG3k2tREa_pyg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCXax9xkuopIG3k2tREa_pyg&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClncVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=1adeea37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCXax9xkuopIG3k2tREa_pyg</a><br />\n<br />\nApple Music<br />\n<a href=\"https://music.apple.com/gb/artist/the-merciful-descendant/1033149011\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmusic.apple.com%2Fgb%2Fartist%2Fthe-merciful-descendant%2F1033149011&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClncVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=66db6bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://music.apple.com/gb/artist/the-merciful-descendant/1033149011</a><br />\n<br />\nSpotify<br />\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/artist/4LPxejj199kZa86BiH1ryG?si=aWQnjWmjSWi1CZRdHlJ9Ig&amp;nd=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fartist%2F4LPxejj199kZa86BiH1ryG%3Fsi%3DaWQnjWmjSWi1CZRdHlJ9Ig%26nd%3D1&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClncVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=f48acc5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/artist/4LPxejj199kZa86BiH1ryG?si=aWQnjWmjSWi1CZRdHlJ9Ig&amp;nd=1</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b772d445b5e229b8bbaa2cbf074e16c20fb8deae","tid":2499951,"uid":364068,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"香港近年不斷受到政治打壓，就連瑞典籍的網絡男歌手The Merciful Descendant都對事件表示關於，日前為香港創作新歌《(Hong Kong) Bastion of Light》，並於YouTube及Spotify上推出。<br />\n<br />\nThe Merciful Descendant在個人簡介上自稱是唱作歌手，而且更是所有電腦的標籤，表現其多元化和包容性，有網民指他來自瑞典。The Merciful Descendant在兩周前推出特別為香港創作的歌曲《(Hong Kong) Bastion of Light》，惹來不少網民關注，紛紛感謝他對香港的支持，歌曲中一句歌詞「history will remember their fight（歷史將會記得他們的戰鬥），獲網民回應：「香港教育局已正在篡改歷史，在歷史書上將所有對政府的反抗行動寫成顛覆。你的歌曲將會成為其中一個紀錄，讓我們的孩子了解香港由2019年至今所發生的事情。感謝你，對我們非常有意義。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《(Hong Kong) Bastion of Light》歌詞：</strong><br />\n<br />\nBorn out of greed of the west, now failing the test.<br />\n<br />\nStanding up to the beast and on the world it will feast.<br />\n<br />\nDon&rsquo;t you remember Tiananmen Square, through children, student, parents the bullets teared.<br />\n<br />\nWe failed them then and now again. Hong Kong the last bastion has fallen.<br />\n<br />\nThrough beatings, prison and pandemic they fought.<br />\n<br />\nFor the right to their own mind, will and thought.<br />\n<br />\nOne day when it all comes crashing down, history will remember their fight.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong the last bastion of light.<br />\n<br />\nYou Don&rsquo;t even have the right to believe, no then you soon may stop to breathe.<br />\n<br />\nkilling the Uyghurs for what they hold true, nazi propaganda through and through.<br />\n<br />\nDon&rsquo;t you remember the camps of the war, starts on their arms that&rsquo;s what they wore.<br />\n<br />\nWe failed them then and now again.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong the last bastion has fallen.<br />\n<br />\nThrough beatings, prison and pandemic they fought.<br />\n<br />\nFor the right to their own mind, will and thought.<br />\n<br />\nOne day when it all comes crashing down, history will remember their fight.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong the last bastion of light.<br />\n<br />\nNo law or threat will make them end.<br />\n<br />\nTheir right to freedom they still defend.<br />\n<br />\nThrough beatings, prison and pandemic we fight.<br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s our right for our own mind, will and right.<br />\n<br />\nSoon one day when it all comes crashing down, we shall remember this fight.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong the last bastion of light.<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong the last bastion of light."},{"pid":"87f0115c8654d4159a7af572e73e04b6e18c6db7","tid":2499951,"uid":364068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:24:29.000Z","msg":"follow like CLS 佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b0ceff27459e1ffa6d9040c56d9e6690828b55","tid":2499951,"u